about 42&lt;br&gt;
&gt; warnings that might be of interest to the project. You can launch
an&lt;br&gt;
&gt; instance of FindBugs and evaluate each warning using this link
(requires&lt;br&gt;
&gt; Java): &lt;a moz-do-not-send=&quot;true&quot;
