&gt; comment on any warning by signing into a Google, Yahoo or OpenID
account)&lt;br&gt;
&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&gt; FindBugs has recently started a community review of several open
source&lt;br&gt;
&gt; projects. This is similar to a recently completed review&lt;br&gt;
&gt; &lt;&lt;a moz-do-not-send=&quot;true&quot;
